26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_fb_g84.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "nv50.h"
30#include "ram.h"
31
32static const struct nv50_fb_func
33g84_fb = {
34 .ram_new = nv50_ram_new,
35 .trap = 0x001d07ff,
36};
37
38int
39g84_fb_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_fb **pfb)
40{
41 return nv50_fb_new_(&g84_fb, device, index, pfb);
42}
